Interface RealArray

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DoubleArray

    public interface RealArray
    A RealArray is a 2D real valued array.

      • stringToArray

        static double[][] stringToArray(String string)
                         throws BadArrayException
        Returns a double[][] with the values and dimensions specified in the input String. The input String may consist of real numbers (use "." as the decimal point), whitespace as column separators and semicolons as row separators. Jagged arrays are disallowed: all rows must have the same number of elements.
        Parameters:
        string - a String representation of the array
        Returns:
        the corresponding array
        Throws:
        BadArrayException - if the input is invalid

      • stringToRow
